title: Josie Dixon: The state of palliative care [Video]
itunes:author: Josie Dixon
description: Contributor(s): Josie Dixon | A major report released by LSE reveals widespread inequities in the UK’s palliative care system, with key groups missing out and large gaps in services, communication and responsibilities.
